ivardefs.name: documentation
ivardefs.desc: A description of how the application supports or uses the specified document profile.  For example, when documents are created, what action is taken with consumed documents, etc.

ivardefs.name: mode
ivardefs.desc: Mode of this document declaration - whether an application is a producer or consumer.

ivardefs.name: profile
ivardefs.desc: A profile on the document Bundle that constrains which resources are present, and their contents.
